F_{x}(n)=P(X=n)=\frac{c}{n(n+1)}
c
P(X>m)
m=1,2,3...
\lim\sum\limits_{n \in \mathbb{N}} F_{x}(n)=1 
\lim\sum\limits_{n \in \mathbb{N}} F_{x}(n)=\frac{c}{n(n+1)} + \frac{c}{(n+1)(n+2)} ... \leq c(\frac{1}{2}+\frac{1}{4} ...)\leq c
c
1
P(X>m)
\frac{1}{n\left(n+1\right)}=\frac{1}{n}-\frac{1}{n+1}
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{1}{n\left(n+1\right)}=\lim_{m\rightarrow\infty}\sum_{n=1}^{m}\frac{1}{n\left(n+1\right)}=\lim_{m\rightarrow\infty}\sum_{n=1}^{m}\left(\frac{1}{n}-\frac{1}{n+1}\right)=\lim_{m\rightarrow\infty}1-\frac{1}{m+1}=1
c
S=\sum\limits_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{n(n+1)}
c=\frac{1}{S}
P\{x>m\}=c\sum\limits_{i=m+1}^\infty \frac{1}{n(n+1)}
